Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on the performance analysis of indoor millimetre-wave networks, which is a networking topic. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the area spectral efficiency of the network, which is a topic related to information theory. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the use of millimetre-wave communications, which is a topic related to multimedia. 
4. cs.AR (Augmented Reality) - The paper discusses the use of directional antennas pointing downwards to illuminate selected spots on the ground, which is a topic related to augmented reality. 
5. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper discusses the impact of densification and body blockage on the achievable performance, which is a topic related to multi-agent systems.
